  "_integrationTestNotes": "Integration tests should verify: (1) Activity_0jg58ef (Get credit score) calls real credit bureau API with applicant details; (2) Activity_19tmw4x (Validate data and create ticket) calls real ticket system; (3) Activity_00toffi (DMN — calculate_loan_results_01uhf55) evaluates real rules with creditScore, loan.amount, loan.tenure, pi.annual_salary; (4) Activity_1qx00c8 (Send offer via mail) sends real email offer; (5) Activity_0ytx2e1 (Customer accepts offer) receives real customer response (receiveTask, message: customer_accepts_offer, correlationKey=ticketId); (6) Activity_0neec1e (Provide loan) calls real loan disbursement system. Key flow: decline paths (auto or manual) throw error Error_1waf4p2 → caught by error boundary on sub-process → event sub-process Activity_18spil4 triggered → must complete Activity_06izmqr (Send rejection mail) and Activity_02ronq9 (Record declined loan). Note: loan-underwriting-form.form must be deployed."
